4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning course. In just 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics to become professional Data Analysts. They will also gain experience in creating predictive models using popular libraries such as Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. With a focus on practical application, students will solve real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The course is suitable for beginners as no previous experience is required. Classes are held three times a week with a maximum class size of 12 students. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. Both English and Spanish syllabus options are available. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop